{"word":"Dedication","slug":"dedication","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dedication</b> Law concerning dedicated things<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27'>Lev 27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=14'>Num 18:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=27'>1Ch 26:27</a> <br/> - Must be without blemish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=23'>Lev 22:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=1&verse=14'>Mal 1:14</a> <br/> - Not redeemable<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=27&verse=29'>Lev 27:29</a> <br/> - Offering must be voluntary<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=1&verse=3'>Lev 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=19'>Lev 22:19</a><br/><a href='S:Offerings'>Offerings</a>; <a href='S:Vows'>Vows</a> <br/> Of the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7'>Num 7</a><br/> Solomon's temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8'>1Ki 8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=5'>2Ch 7:5</a><br/> Second temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=6&verse=17'>Ezr 6:17</a><br/> Of the wall of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=43'>Neh 12:43</a><br/> Of houses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=5'>Deu 20:5</a><br/> Of Samuel by his mother<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=11'>1Sa 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=22'>1Sa 1:22</a><br/><a href='S:Consecration'>Consecration</a><br/> For instances of liberality in dedicated things<br/> <a href='S:Liberality'>Liberality</a><br/> Feast of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=22'>Joh 10:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=65'>1Ki 8:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=10'>2Ch 7:10</a>"}]}